address.streetAddress: Abington Plan, The Meadows At Shannon Lakes

location.fullValue: Abington Plan, The Meadows At Shannon Lakes

data.description: Outstanding, like-new 2-story, built in 2020, with quality upgrades throughout. Beautiful home in the Village at Shannon Green, minutes from shopping & business areas, with easy access to SR 33, I-70 & 270. Wonderful curb appeal with stone accented exterior & covered Front Porch. Open design living area with expansive, flexible design Great Room, & beautifully appointed Kitchen, plus a separate front formal Dining Rm or Den/Office. 9' ceilings, upgraded flooring, lighting & more. Kitchen features 42'' espresso cabinets, ss appliances, island with breakfast bar, pantry, Eating Area with sliding glass door to the Patio. Elegant Primary Suite with tray ceiling, 2 walk-in closets & private Bath with dbl sinks & shower. 2 additional BRs, multi-purpose Loft, Full Bath & Laundry Rm. Welcome Home!
